trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of warnings produced by <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import(System.CodeDom.CodeNamespace,System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit)"></xref>.

Specifies that no proxy class was generated by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import(System.CodeDom.CodeNamespace,System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit)"></xref> method.

Specifies that the proxy class generated by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import(System.CodeDom.CodeNamespace,System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit)"></xref> method includes no methods.

Specifies that at least one optional <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension"></xref> for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> to be imported has been ignored.

Specifies that at least one required <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension"></xref> for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> to be imported has been ignored.
Specifies that the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> schema is invalid.

Specifies that at least one <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Binding"></xref> for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> to be imported is of an unsupported type and has been ignored.

Specifies that at least one <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Operation"></xref> for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> to be imported is of an unsupported type and has been ignored.
Specifies that the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> to be imported does not conform to the WS-I Basic Profile.
